OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,FSaturday morning with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, drier and brighter later. Cloudy
OL,8,Fand windy at times Sunday and Monday
OL,9,Fwith occasional spells of rain,
OL,10,Fstaying drier in east.
